snippet.title: To the Crown - my game in Gdevelop 5
snippet.description:
Happy New Year guys! :)
Well, my first game is finally finished! Wanna say - 
Thank you to everybody who supported me! I'm very appreciate it:)
And huge thanks to Gdevelop team for their engine:)

To the Crown on Itch.io - https://nt-exe.itch.io/to-the-crown
My Twitter - https://twitter.com/NT_exeGames
